The number of injured in the task $j$
The cost of rescuing per injured in the state $\lambda$
The time it takes for the injured to transit from state $\lambda$ to $\lambda+1$ completely
The travel time from workstation to task $j$, workstation is the starting point of rescue teams

The fatigue factor for the rescue team $i$
